  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Emergency Relief Support to River Eroded People of Naria, Shariatpur (HAI)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">People affected by river erosion were able to re-settle their location and bought necessary materials and emergency food for their families. On the other, people with disability received assistive devices for easy movement. Hygiene kits and materials greatly helped them to maintain personal hygiene and meet the family crisis.</narrative>
  </description>
